column2: SELECT TOP #   a.OBJID AS OBJID,   a.RA AS RA,   a.DEC AS DEC,      gsl.specObjID AS sdssid_galspecline,   gsl.z AS Z,   gsl.zErr AS e_Z,   gsl.zWarning AS zWarning,   gsl.nii_#_flux AS NII_#_FLUX,   gsl.sii_#_flux AS SII_#_FLUX,   gsl.oi_#_flux AS OI_#_FLUX,   gsl.oiii_#_flux AS OIII_#_FLUX,   gsl.h_alpha_flux AS H_ALPHA_FLUX,   gsl.h_beta_flux AS H_BETA_FLUX,      gsl.nii_#_flux_err AS NII_#_flux_err,   gsl.sii_#_flux_err AS SII_#_flux_err,   gsl.oi_#_flux_err AS OI_#_flux_err,   gsl.oiii_#_flux_err AS OIII_#_flux_err,   gsl.h_alpha_flux_err AS H_ALPHA_flux_err,   gsl.h_beta_flux_err AS H_BETA_flux_err,    o.distance AS SEPARATION_AKARI_SDSS8       FROM   MyDB.akari AS a      /* INTO mydb.final_catalog_lines */   OUTER APPLY dbo.fGetNearestSpecObjAllEq( a.RA, a.DEC, #) AS o   LEFT JOIN galSpecLine AS gsl ON o.specObjID = gsl.specObjID    WHERE   a.OBJID = #
